description: This is a React component for a dashboard page in a front-end web application, built with Next.js and TypeScript. It manages user dashboard data, including usage, account, subscription info, and recent images, rendering corresponding UI elements.

methods.name: DashboardPage
methods.description: Main React component that renders the user dashboard, fetching and displaying data such as usage, account info, subscription, and recent images, with controls for managing subscription plans, uploading images, and navigation.
